>  >
>  >I note that the Soyo web site has published a BIOS upgrade for the
>  >SY-5EMA which deals with Linux shutdown issue.
>  >
>  >The SY-5EHM also exhibits this problem - on shutdown a page fault is
>  >reported in the halt process during last stages of shutdown. This is
> due
>  >to the BIOS attempting to resolve a real address whilst still in
>  >protected mode. Windows 95 doesn't exhibit this problem because it
>  >switches to real mode prior to calling the BIOS routine.
>  >
>  >Please supply a revised BIOS (I suppose this will be similar to the
> 5EMA
>  >fix) to fix this problem.
